322
00:16:47,958 --> 00:16:51,292
Your body isn't injured at all, right?

323
00:16:51,292 --> 00:16:53,417
It's all thanks to magic.

324
00:16:53,417 --> 00:16:56,083
It really doesn't hurt.

325
00:16:56,083 --> 00:16:59,500
