348
00:17:50,125 --> 00:17:51,042
Sexual harassment.

349
00:17:51,042 --> 00:17:52,542
It'd be nice if you had a better personality.

350
00:17:52,542 --> 00:17:54,375
It's my turn. My turn.

351
00:17:54,375 --> 00:17:56,500
I'm not a sandbag.

352
00:17:56,500 --> 00:18:00,292
Forget it. Thanks to Carla's magic,
I can finally fight you this time.

353
00:18:00,292 --> 00:18:02,042
And I have a sword in my hand.

354
00:18:02,042 --> 00:18:03,792
